```
In GJS templates, `this.taskName.isRunning` is directly accessible and reactive. You can use it inside `{{#if}}` to conditionally render spinners, skeleton loaders, or alternative button labels. The template re-renders automatically as `isRunning` changes ŌĆö no manual state management required.

```gjs
import Component from '@glimmer/component'
import { task, timeout } from 'ember-concurrency'
import { registerDestructor } from '@ember/destroyable'

export default class ScoreTrackerComponent extends Component {
  constructor(owner, args) {
