```
`task.last.error` holds the error thrown by the last task execution that failed. Use the three-state pattern in templates: check `isRunning`, then `last.error`, then `last.value`. This gives full control over loading, error, and success UI states without any manual `@tracked` error variable.

```gjs
import Component from '@glimmer/component'
