Both `fetch` calls are fired simultaneously with `Promise.all`, cutting total wait time nearly in half compared to sequential fetching. The two JSON parsing steps are also parallelised in a second `Promise.all`. The combined object merges both datasets with computed derived fields (`teamSize`, `captainName`), creating a single reactive `dashboard` reference for the template.

